title: Greece Car Registrations
description: Car Registrations in Greece decreased to 7801 in October from 8608 in September of 2022. Car Registrations in Greece averaged 13619.47  from 1989 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 33583  in January of 2008 and a record low of 2434  in April of 2020. This page provides the latest reported value for - Greece Car Registrations - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Hellenic Association of Motor Vehicle Importers-Representatives
